text: The Wests Tigers are an Australian professional rugby league team. The team is based in the Inner West of Sydney, New South Wales. They were founded in 1999. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have won one premiership in 2005 against the North Queensland Cowboys. ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports clubs and teams in Sydney Category:1999 establishments in Australia
